  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ensure a high standard of clinical practice and conduct, and participate actively in pursuing continual professional development</li>\n  <li>Work independently in managing complex cases and be professionally accredited to perform physiotherapy therapy procedures for specialised patient cohorts</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree/Diploma in Physiotherapy </li>\n  <li>Member of the Singapore Physiotherapy Association</li>\n  <li> 1 - 2 years relevant experience would be preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Interested candidates can write in to Ann at anngoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ann Goh Xin Ting<br>\nR1875289</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br>\nE.A License: 99C4599</strong></p>",
